  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    BadPasswordException
    An attempt to set a password that fails the PasswordRuleChecker in place.
    NonUniqueCredentialsException
    An attempt to persist a Principal failed because at least one of the Credentials was not unique for all AuthenticationDomains the principal is part of.
